es enabled'=>'ເປີດການອັບເດດອັດຕະໂນມັດແລ້ວ','Are pretty permalinks supported?'=>'ຮອງຮັບລິ້ງຖາວອນແບບສວຍງາມ (Pretty Permalinks) ຫຼື ບໍ່?','PHP memory limit (only for admin screens)'=>'ຂີດຈຳກັດໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ PHP (ສະເພາະໜ້າຈໍຜູ້ດູແລ)','Is this site discouraging search engines?'=>'ເວັບໄຊນີ້ກຳລັງຂັດຂວາງເຄື່ອງມືຄົ້ນຫາຢູ່ ຫຼື ບໍ່?','Wide Blocks'=>'ບລັອກແບບກວ້າງ (Wide Blocks)','Block Editor Styles'=>'ຮູບແບບຕົວແກ້ໄຂບລັອກ (Block Editor Styles)','Spam'=>'ສະແປມ','Unable to write to %s file.'=>'ບໍ່ສາມາດຂຽນລົງໃນໄຟລ໌ %s ໄດ້.','<strong>Error:</strong> The %s options page is not in the allowed options list.'=>'<strong>ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ:</strong> ໜ້າຕົວເລືອກ %s ບໍ່ຢູ່ໃນລາຍການຕົວເລືອກທີ່ອະນຸຍາດ.','Error:'=>'ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ:','You should update your %s file now.'=>'ເຈົ້າຄວນອັບເດດໄຟລ໌ %s ຂອງເຈົ້າດຽວນີ້.','This localized version contains both the translation and various other localization fixes.'=>'ເວີຊັນທ້ອງຖິ່ນນີ້ປະກອບມີທັງຄຳແປ ແລະ ການແກ້ໄຂການປັບແຕ່ງທ້ອງຖິ່ນອື່ນໆ.','Take a look at the <strong>%1$d item</strong> on the <a href="%2$s">Site Health screen</a>.'=>'ກວດສອບ <strong>%1$d ລາຍການ</strong> ໃນ <a href="%2$s">ໜ້າຈໍສຸຂະພາບເວັບໄຊ</a>.','Your site&#8217;s health is looking good, but there are still some things you can do to improve its performance and security.'=>'ສຸຂະພາບເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າເບິ່ງຄືວ່າດີ, ແຕ່ຍັງມີບາງສິ່ງທີ່ເຈົ້າສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ເພື່ອປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບ ແລະ ຄວາມປອດໄພໃຫ້ດີຂຶ້ນ.','Great job! Your site currently passes all site health checks.'=>'ເຮັດໄດ້ດີຫຼາຍ! ເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າຜ່ານການກວດສອບສຸຂະພາບທັງໝົດໃນຂະນະນີ້.','Your site has critical issues that should be addressed as soon as possible to improve its performance and security.'=>'ເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າມີບັນຫາຮ້າຍແຮງທີ່ຄວນໄດ້ຮັບການແກ້ໄຂໂດຍໄວທີ່ສຸດ ເພື່ອປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບ ແລະ ຄວາມປອດໄພ.','Site health checks will automatically run periodically to gather information about your site. You can also <a href="%s">visit the Site Health screen</a> to gather information about your site now.'=>'ການກວດສອບສຸຂະພາບເວັບໄຊຈະເຮັດວຽກໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເປັນໄລຍະ ເພື່ອເກັບກຳຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າ. ເຈົ້າຍັງສາມາດ <a href="%s">ເຂົ້າເບິ່ງໜ້າຈໍສຸຂະພາບເວັບໄຊ</a> ເພື່ອເກັບກຳຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າໃນຕອນນີ້.','No information yet&hellip;'=>'ຍັງບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນ&hellip;','The uploaded file exceeds the %1$s directive in %2$s.'=>'ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ອັບໂຫຼດມີຂະໜາດເກີນຄຳສັ່ງ %1$s ໃນ %2$s.','No comments found in Trash.'=>'ບໍ່ພົບຄຳຄິດເຫັນໃນຖັງຂີ້ເຫຍື້ອ.','File is empty. Please upload something more substantial. This error could also be caused by uploads being disabled in your %1$s file or by %2$s being defined as smaller than %3$s in %1$s.'=>'ໄຟລ໌ວ່າງເປົ່າ. ກະລຸນາອັບໂຫຼດໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນຫຼາຍກວ່ານີ້. ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດນີ້ອາດຈະເກີດຈາກການປິດການອັບໂຫຼດໃນໄຟລ໌ %1$s ຂອງເຈົ້າ ຫຼື ມີການກຳນົດ %2$s ໃຫ້ນ້ອຍກວ່າ %3$s ໃນ %1$s.','A test is unavailable'=>'ການທົດສອບບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ','Error: %1$s (%2$s)'=>'ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ: %1$s (%2$s)','Your site is running on an older version of PHP (%s), which should be updated'=>'ເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າກຳລັງໃຊ້ PHP ເວີຊັນເກົ່າ (%s), ເຊິ່ງຄວນຈະໄດ້ຮັບການອັບເດດ','Your site is running on an older version of PHP (%s)'=>'ເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າກຳລັງໃຊ້ PHP ເວີຊັນເກົ່າ (%s)','Your site is running a recommended version of PHP (%s)'=>'ເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າກຳລັງໃຊ້ PHP ເວີຊັນທີ່ແນະນຳ (%s)','No media files found in Trash.'=>'ບໍ່ພົບໄຟລ໌ສື່ໃນຖັງຂີ້ເຫຍື້ອ.','%1$s %2$d – %3$s %4$d, %5$d'=>'%2$d %1$s – %4$d %3$s, %5$d','upcoming events year formatY'=>'Y','upcoming events day formatj'=>'j','%1$s %2$d–%3$d, %4$d'=>'%2$d–%3$d %1$s, %4$d','upcoming events month formatF'=>'F','Resend confirmation requests'=>'ສົ່ງຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍການຢືນຢັນຄືນໃໝ່','Delete requests'=>'ລຶບຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍ','Table prefix'=>'ຄຳນຳໜ້າຕາຕະລາງ (Table prefix)','PHP Default Timezone'=>'ເຂດເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງ PHP','PHP default timezone was changed after WordPress loading by a %s function call. This interferes with correct calculations of dates and times.'=>'ເຂດເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງ PHP ຖືກປ່ຽນແປງຫຼັງຈາກ WordPress ໂຫຼດ ໂດຍການເອີ້ນໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ %s. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະລົບກວນການຄິດໄລ່ວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ.','PHP default timezone is invalid'=>'ເຂດເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງ PHP ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ','PHP default timezone was configured by WordPress on loading. This is necessary for correct calculations of dates and times.'=>'ເຂດເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງ PHP ຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໂດຍ WordPress ໃນຂະນະທີ່ໂຫຼດ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈຳເປັນສຳລັບການຄິດໄລ່ວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ.','PHP default timezone is valid'=>'ເຂດເວລາເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງ PHP ຖືກຕ້ອງ','The seventh parameter passed to %s should be numeric representing menu position.'=>'ພາລາມິເຕີທີເຈັດທີ່ສົ່ງໄປຫາ %s ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກທີ່ສະແດງເຖິງຕຳແໜ່ງເມນູ.','The update cannot be installed because WordPress %1$s requires the %2$s PHP extension.'=>'ບໍ່ສາມາດຕິດຕັ້ງການອັບເດດໄດ້ ເນື່ອງຈາກ WordPress %1$s ຕ້ອງການສ່ວນຂະຫຍາຍ PHP %2$s.','https://wordpress.org/about/stats/'=>'https://wordpress.org/about/stats/','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-export-screen/">Documentation on Export</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-export-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການສົ່ງອອກ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-add-new-screen/">Documentation on Installing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-add-new-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການຕິດຕັ້ງປັກອິນ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/pages-screen/">Documentation on Managing Pages</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/pages-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການຈັດການໜ້າ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/posts-screen/">Documentation on Managing Posts</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/posts-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການຈັດການໂພສ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/settings-discussion-screen/">Documentation on Discussion Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/settings-discussion-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າການສົນທະນາ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-themes-screen/#install-themes">Documentation on Adding New Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-themes-screen/#install-themes">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການເພີ່ມທີມໃໝ່</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/media-add-new-screen/">Documentation on Uploading Media Files</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/media-add-new-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການອັບໂຫຼດໄຟລ໌ສື່</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/roles-and-capabilities/">Descriptions of Roles and Capabilities</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/roles-and-capabilities/">ຄຳອະທິບາຍກ່ຽວກັບບົດບາດ ແລະ ສິດການໃຊ້ງານ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/users-screen/">Documentation on Managing Users</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/users-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການຈັດການຜູ້ໃຊ້</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/users-your-profile-screen/">Documentation on User Profiles</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/users-your-profile-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຜູ້ໃຊ້</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/settings-media-screen/">Documentation on Media Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/settings-media-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າສື່</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-import-screen/">Documentation on Import</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-import-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການນຳເຂົ້າ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-screen/">Documentation on Tools</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບເຄື່ອງມື</a>','This page allows direct access to your site settings. You can break things here. Please be cautious!'=>'ໜ້ານີ້ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ເຂົ້າເຖິງການຕັ້ງຄ່າເວັບໄຊຂອງເຈົ້າໂດຍກົງ. ເຈົ້າອາດຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ລະບົບເສຍຫາຍໄດ້ຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້. ກະລຸນາລະມັດລະວັງ!','<strong>Format</strong> &mdash; Post Formats designate how your theme will display a specific post. For example, you could have a <em>standard</em> blog post with a title and paragraphs, or a short <em>aside</em> that omits the title and contains a short text blurb. Your theme could enable all or some of 10 possible formats. <a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/advanced-administration/wordpress/post-formats/#supported-formats">Learn more about each post format</a>.'=>'<strong>ຮູບແບບ</strong> &mdash; ຮູບແບບໂພສກຳນົດວ່າທີມຂອງເຈົ້າຈະສະແດງໂພສໃດໜຶ່ງແນວໃດ. ຕົວຢ່າງ, ເຈົ້າອາດຈະມີໂພສບລັອກແບບ <em>ມາຕະຖານ</em> ທີ່ມີຫົວຂໍ້ ແລະ ຫຍໍ້ໜ້າ, ຫຼື <em>ໝາຍເຫດ (aside)</em> ສັ້ນໆ ທີ່ບໍ່ມີຫົວຂໍ້ ແລະ ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມສັ້ນໆ. ທີມຂອງເຈົ້າສາມາດເປີດໃຊ້ທັງໝົດ ຫຼື ບາງສ່ວນຂອງ 10 ຮູບແບບທີ່ເປັນໄປໄດ້. <a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/advanced-administration/wordpress/post-formats/#supported-formats">ຮຽນຮູ້ເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບແຕ່ລະຮູບແບບໂພສ</a>.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/pages-screen/">Documentation on Editing Pages</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/pages-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການແກ້ໄຂໜ້າ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/pages-add-new-screen/">Documentation on Adding New Pages</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/pages-add-new-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການເພີ່ມໜ້າໃໝ່</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/media-library-screen/">Documentation on Media Library</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/media-library-screen/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບຄັງສື່</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/revisions/">Revisions Management</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/revisions/">ການຈັດການສະບັບແກ້ໄຂ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/edit-media/">Documentation on Edit Media</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/edit-media/">ເອກະສານກ່ຽວກັບການແກ້ໄຂສື່</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/manage-plugins/">Documentation on Managing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/manage-plugins/